and go home now.

1147
00:53:27,027 --> 00:53:28,229
Right, Sister Barnes?

1148
00:53:32,502 --> 00:53:33,597
Sister?

1149
00:53:34,440 --> 00:53:35,632
(WATER POURING)

1150
00:53:37,134 --> 00:53:38,470
Sister Barnes?

1151
00:53:39,405 --> 00:53:42,110
I think we should listen
to our super neat

1152
00:53:42,212 --> 00:53:45,747
