and choose the right door?

1153
00:53:45,849 --> 00:53:47,717
You know, choose the "right"?

1154
00:53:47,819 --> 00:53:48,978
Like they taught us
in primary?

1155
00:53:49,080 --> 00:53:50,554
It doesn't...

1156
