1195
00:55:38,459 --> 00:55:40,361
So it doesn't matter
what I believe, does it?

1196
00:55:43,030 --> 00:55:44,396
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

1197
00:55:44,499 --> 00:55:47,137
Sister Paxton, do you still
believe in God?

1198
00:55:48,098 --> 00:55:49,271
Yes.

1199
00:55:50,974 --> 00:55:52,439
Then let's leave through here.

1200
00:55:53,372 --> 00:55:55,979
Let's be honest and sincere

1201
00:55:56,081 --> 00:55:58,577
and let God decide
what happens next for us.

1202
00:56:01,049 --> 00:56:03,219
(PAXTON BREATHING HEAVILY)

1203
00:56:06,087 --> 00:56:08,389
(DOOR OPENS AND CREAKS)

1204
00:56:13,226 --> 00:56:15,194
Okay, we're leaving now.

1205
00:56:15,296 --> 00:56:17,164
Thank you
for all your mentorship,

1206
00:56:17,266 --> 00:56:19,400
and thank you
for letting us leave.

1207
00:56:26,106 --> 00:56:28,343
(FOOTSTEPS RECEDING)

1208
00:56:29,813 --> 00:56:31,043
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

1209
00:56:31,145 --> 00:56:33,348
(OMINOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

1210
00:56:47,864 --> 00:56:49,628
Are you coming too?

1211
00:56:56,675 --> 00:56:57,639
(DOOR CREAKING)

1212
00:56:57,741 --> 00:56:59,341
(DOOR SHUTS)

1213
