we challenge him.

1238
00:58:43,342 --> 00:58:45,146
We make him think.

1239
00:58:45,248 --> 00:58:47,215
He doesn't have
to steam roll us.

1240
00:58:47,317 --> 00:58:48,744
We might not
be a physical threat,

1241
00:58:48,846 --> 00:58:50,716
