- (BREATHING HEAVILY)

1245
00:59:03,899 --> 00:59:05,662
(GRUNTS)

1246
00:59:05,764 --> 00:59:08,397
I think that window
has a cage on it.

1247
00:59:08,499 --> 00:59:10,406
